    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>White pigment made of bismuth nitrate or sometimes bismuth chloride oxide. It is used in  cosmetics, ceramic glazes, surface coatings, and enamels. </Note_Text>
